    <fields>
        <fullName>AvailabilityExceptions</fullName>
        <inlineHelpText>The non-standard days off for this facility, like public holidays and emergency time off. For instance, if your facility isn&apos;t available on election day, you can specify that here, but you don&apos;t need to list down weekend days off.</inlineHelpText>
